# Get Comment by ID

Retrieves a specific comment by its ID.

## Endpoint

```
CopyGET http://localhost:8080/comment/getCommentById/{id}

 ```

## Path Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| id | integer | The unique identifier of the comment |

## Example Request

```
GET http://localhost:8080/comment/getCommentById/10

 ```

## Response

### Success Response

**Code:** 200 OK

**Content example**

```
{
    "id": 10,
    "postId": 3,
    "commentBody": "tesssttttt2",
    "commentCreateDate": "2024-10-10T15:07:41.911231Z",
    "commentCreateBy": "Chie"
}

 ```
